          <p class="font-sans text-brand-ink-3 mb-2" style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em">板橋店｜雙十路二段 47 巷 28 號</p>
          <iframe
            src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=新北市板橋區雙十路二段47巷28號&output=embed&hl=zh-TW&z=16"
            width="100%" height="220" style="border:0;display:block"
            allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="能見度眼鏡 × 能見度驗光所 板橋地圖"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

